These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, mirinda, milk
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, metal, country
1. the fan of metal is the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person drinking milk is between the fan of country and the person drinking mirinda##2
3. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the fan of ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Beverage      | mirinda | milk | coffee |
| Music-Genre   | metal     | ambient    | country   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: reading, gardening, baking
The people have 3 different jobs:  firefighter, engineer, lawyer
1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the lawyer is between the firefighter and the person who's hobby is reading##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Hobby   | reading    | baking        | gardening |
| Job     | engineer | lawyer | firefighter         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, almond-milk, water
3 different pets are kept: mouse, rabbit, lizard
1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking sprite is between the owner of the rabbit and the person drinking water##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | sprite     | water |
| Pet        | rabbit  | lizard | mouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: trance, folk, metal
3 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, horse
1. the fan of trance is the owner of the cat##1
2. the fan of metal is between the owner of the ferret and the owner of the cat##2
3. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | folk  | metal     | trance |
| Pet           | ferret | horse | cat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: gardening, chess, board-games
3 different pets are kept: snake, goldfish, horse
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
3. the owner of the snake is between the owner of the horse and the owner of the goldfish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Hobby   | chess | board-games     | gardening |
| Pet     | horse    | snake | goldfish    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
There are 3 different nationalities: thai, canadian, malaysian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, cycling, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is baseball is between the malaysian and the thai##2
2. the thai is the person who's sport is cycling##1
3. the canadian is on the right of the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Nationality   | thai  | canadian   | malaysian        |
| Sport         | cycling | baseball | water-polo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
There 3 different types of food: pepper, spinach, banana
There are 3 different nationalities: pakistani, australian, malaysian
1. the person eating banana is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
2. the pakistani is between the person eating banana and the australian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | spinach  | pepper  | banana |
| Nationality   | australian | pakistani | malaysian     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: martial-arts, fantasy, musical
There are 3 different nationalities: japanese, american, chinese
1. the person watching fantasy movies is the chinese##1
2. the american is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person watching musical movies##2
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical   | martial-arts  | fantasy  |
| Nationality   | japanese | american | chinese |

