.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, lacrosse, rugby
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, helicopter, train
1. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the person driving the roller is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person driving the helicopter##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Sport       | rugby | biathlon | lacrosse  |
| Transport   | train    | roller        | helicopter |

