.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-11::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, lemonade, cola
There 3 different types of food: raspberry, apricot, banana
1. the person eating banana is between the person drinking lemonade and the person eating raspberry##2
2. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| Beverage   | lemonade | water      | cola      |
| Food       | apricot  | banana | raspberry |

