The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, weightlifting, tennis
1. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | dubstep   | metal   |
| Sport         | weightlifting | tennis | lacrosse |

