1. the person watching crime movies is between the fan of funk and the person watching sports movies##2
2. the fan of pop is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | crime | martial-arts |
| Music-Genre   | salsa    | pop | funk   |

