.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, fanta, almond-milk
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, blues, r&b
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
2. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking almond-milk and the fan of blues##2
3. the fan of metal is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | fanta   | mirinda |
| Music-Genre   | r&b  | metal | blues   |

 